data.description: Seller is offering a $5,000 credit to buyer for closing costs, rate buy down, etc., plus 3.25% Assumable Interest Rate! This turn-key 4 bedroom home is move-in ready! The home is situated on a spacious lot with breathtaking mountain views! The interior greets you with a large foyer and open floor plan, including a separate den and a great room. The natural light accentuates the fresh paint (2021) on the walls, baseboards, trim and ceilings! The meticulously maintained home has new flooring on the second floor (2022) and an upgraded staircase (2023). The open-concept design of the great room allows for seamless entertaining. Your large kitchen boasts granite countertops, upgraded cabinetry, an island, walk-in pantry and stainless steel appliances, including a new microwave (2023). storage throughout including a coat closet under the stairs, multiple linen closets throughout and extra storage space in the garage! Outside is a large backyard, a blank canvas with a covered patio. This prime location is just a stone's throw away from top-rated schools, shopping centers, and a variety of dining options. Don't miss out!
